#: ../../B/BiCapitalization.rst:9
msgid ""
"The act said to have been performed on trademarks (such as "
":ref:`PostScript`\\, NeXT, :ref:`NeWS`\\, VisiCalc, FrameMaker, TK!solver, "
"EasyWriter) that have been raised above the ruck of common coinage by "
"nonstandard capitalization. Too many :ref:`marketroid` types think this sort"
" of thing is really cute, even the 2,317th time they do it. Compare "
":ref:`studlycaps`\\, :ref:`InterCaps`\\."
msgstr ""
"非標準の大文字化によってありふれた造語の群れから一段引き上げられた商標(\\ :ref:`PostScript`\\ 、NeXT、\\ "
":ref:`NeWS`\\ "
"、VisiCalc、FrameMaker、TK!solver、EasyWriterなど)に対して施されたとされる行為。あまりに多くの\\ "
":ref:`marketroid`\\ 連中が、2,317回目になってさえ、この種のことを実にかわいいと思っている。\\ "
":ref:`studlycaps`\\ 、\\ :ref:`InterCaps`\\ と比較せよ。"
